title: AIE LABS
description:
AIE is building the best-in-class infrastructure layer to onboard Web2 social entertainment apps to Web3. Starting with AIE’s inaugural apps, and continuously partnering with Web2 applications to bolster our ecosystem.  
Since the launch of our TG BOT on August 1st, we have already amassed over 70K wallets, and 800K transactions with our V1 testnet.  We’re currently deploying our V2 testnet with current stats of +100K wallets and +1M transactions in the past few days (testnet.aielabs.io)
